      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in absolute showroom condition! I have babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m really looking for a great new home for it, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look. You won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
