      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. This example features the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine with its sequential twin-turbocharger system delivering seamless boost throughout the rev range. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its factory-spec 50:50 weight distribution and double-wishbone suspension for telepathic handling. Compression numbers are optimal across all rotor faces, and the five-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision. Finished in its original pigment with a pristine interior, this FD is free of common vacuum line or heat management issues, representing a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector.",
